egent there after his death.  See also  Margery  ,   Marjorie ."],"variants":[{"name":"Margareta","meanings":["From the Latin form of Greek <i>Margarītēs</i>.  See  <b>Margaret</b>   ."]},{"name":"Margaretta","meanings":["Formed from Margaret."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Margaret was born in 1250, in Stirlingshire, Scotland. She married John de la Schaw. They were the parents of at least 1 son."},"et":{"1250–":"1250–Surnud","1250–1296":"1250–1296","1275–1323":"1275–1323","1250–Female":"1250–Surnud","1323":"1323","1275":"1275","1296":"1296","1250":"1250","Scotland":"Scotland","Stirlingshire, Scotland":"Stirlingshire, Scotland"},"fi":{"1250–":"1250–Kuollut","1250–1296":"1250–1296","1275–1323":"1275–1323","1250–Female":"1250–Kuollut","1323":"1323","1275":"1275","1296":"1296","1250":"1250","Scotland":"Scotland","Stirlingshire, Scotland":"Stirlingshire, Scotland"},"fr":{"1250–":"1250–Décédée","1250–1296":"1250–1296","1275–1323":"1275–1323","1250–Female":"1250–Décédée","1323":"1323","1275":"1275","1296":"1296","1250":"1250","Scotland":"Écosse","Stirlingshire, Scotland":"Stirlingshire, Écosse","lifeSummary":"Margaret est née en 1250, à Stirlingshire, Écosse. Elle a épousé John de la Schaw. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fils."},"de":{"1250–":"1250–Verstorben","1250–1296":"1250–1296","1275–1323":"1275–1323","1250–Female":"1250–Verstorben","1323":"1323","1275":"1275","1296":"1296","1250":"1250","Scotland":"Scotland","Stirlingshire, Scotland":"Stirlingshire, Scotland","lifeSummary":"Margaret wurde 1250 in Stirlingshire, Scotland geboren. Sie hat John de la Schaw geheiratet. Sie hatten mindestens 1 Sohn."},"ht":{"1250–":"1250–Desede","1250–1296":"1250–1296","1275–1323":"1275–1323","1250–Female":"1250–Desede","1323":"1323","1275":"1275","1296":"1296","1250":"1250","Scotland":"Scotland","Stirlingshire, Scotland":"Stirlingshire, Scotland"},"hu":{"1250–":"1250–elhunyt","1250–1296":"1250–1296","1275–1323":"1275–1323","1250–Female":"1250–elhunyt","1323":"1323","1275":"1275","1296":"1296","1250":"12